    • Method Detail

      • checkConfigYML

        private void checkConfigYML(@NotNull
                            @NotNull org.bukkit.plugin.Plugin plugin)
        If it does not exist, copy the config.yml from the .jar to the plugin folder and then check that it has all the settings inside. If any are missing, they are added with the default value.
        Parameters:
        plugin - Plugin instance
